r":[],"Configuration":{"InputHeight":28,"InputWidth":100,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"Error","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":7,"QuestionDescription":"Dear participant, you are trying to access this study using a mobile device. Please note that thi...","QuestionID":"QID31","QuestionText":"Dear participant,<br>\nyou are trying to access this study using a mobile device. Please note that this study does not run on mobile devices. If you want to participate, please restart the HIT from a laptop or PC.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Dear participant,<br>\nyou are trying to access this study using a mobile device. Please note that this study does not run on mobile devices. If you want to participate, please restart the HIT from a laptop or PC.","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID188\/DisplayableQuestion\/1","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Dear participant, in the following you will be presented with pictures of cars over several trial...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\"><\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Displayed<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID188\/QuestionDisplayed","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"Displayed","QuestionID":"QID188","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID188","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"Error Text","libraryID":"UR_56E3qwoIP9j8Xnn","messageID":"MS_e4Fm7Y2Zs9ruAcZ","subMessageID":"VE_ERROR"}},"Type":"CustomValidation"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6liMpvgIS8eOlP8","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID32","SecondaryAttribute":"Basic information on data protection Generally, we assess and process your data only after your c...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"Configuration":{"InputHeight":29,"InputWidth":60,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"IC","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":5,"QuestionDescription":"Basic information on data protection Generally, we assess and process your data only after your c...","QuestionID":"QID32","QuestionText":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Basic information on data protection<\/span><\/b><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Generally, we assess and process your data only after your consent. The aim of the assessment and processing of these data is the conduction of this research project. Anonymity and confidentiality of your data is ensured at all times in accordance with current data protection laws as well as psychological research ethics. In this study, you will not be asked to provide any personal or sensitive information that may identify who you are. Within one month after completion of this study, you can send an email to socialcognition@rub.de, and request that we permanently delete the data we have collected from you. The request must include your prolific ID. If you request deletion of your responses, we will permanently delete all of the data that we have collected from you. If you do not request deletion of your data within this one-month period, your responses will be permanently stored on local hard drives and it will be made publicly available on the Open Science Framework (osf.io) for possible secondary data use.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">In case you have questions on this declaration of data protection, please contact the project managers or the data protection officer. According to the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the respective national data protection laws and other regulations, responsible is the Ruhr University Bochum or the leading researcher:<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Prof. Dr. Hans Alves, E-Mail: hans.alves@rub.de.<br \/>\nContact of the data protection officer of the Ruhr University Bochum: phone: +49 (234) 322-8720; email: dsb@rub.de<br \/>\nFurther information on data protection:<br \/>\nhttps:\/\/dsb.ruhr-uni-bochum.de\/<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Declaration of consent<\/span><\/b><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I hereby confirm that I am participating in this study on a voluntary basis. I am aware that I can quit the study at any time without indicating any reasons [by closing the browser window], even before agreeing to this consent form. After completion of the study, I have the right to be informed about the background, aims and results of the study. I am aware that I can assert this right by asking for the relevant information. The corresponding contact address will be indicated at the end of the study. My anonymity will remain assured at all times. Data will be used for scientific purposes only and will be saved only for data analysis. Conclusions regarding individual participants are not possible. My anonymous data will be made available for secondary use by third parties in order to ensure transparency in science. The aim, purpose and extent of this secondary use are not yet foreseeable.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you have read and understood the above-mentioned points and consent to the terms of participation, please<br \/>\n&nbsp;<strong>type the word yes&nbsp;into the text box below<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>and click on &ldquo;Continue&rdquo;<\/strong>.<br \/>\nIf you do not agree, simply close this window.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Basic information on data protection<\/span><\/b><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Generally, we assess and process your data only after your consent. The aim of the assessment and processing of these data is the conduction of this research project. Anonymity and confidentiality of your data is ensured at all times in accordance with current data protection laws as well as psychological research ethics. In this study, you will not be asked to provide any personal or sensitive information that may identify who you are. Within one month after completion of this study, you can send an email to social.cognition@rub.de, and request that we permanently delete the data we have collected from you. The request must include your prolific ID. If you request deletion of your responses, we will permanently delete all of the data that we have collected from you. If you do not request deletion of your data within this one-month period, your responses will be permanently stored on local hard drives and it will be made publicly available on the Open Science Framework (osf.io) for possible secondary data use.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">In case you have questions on this declaration of data protection, please contact the project managers or the data protection officer. According to the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the respective national data protection laws and other regulations, responsible is the Ruhr-University Bochum or the leading researcher:<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Prof. Dr. Hans Alves, E-Mail: halves@asu.edu.<br \/>\nContact of the data protection officer of the Ruhr-University Bochum: phone: +49 (234) 322-8720; email: dsb@rub.de<br \/>\nFurther information on data protection:<br \/>\nhttps:\/\/dsb.ruhr-uni-bochum.de\/<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%\">Declaration of consent<\/span><\/b><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I hereby confirm that I am participating in this study on a voluntary basis. I am aware that I can quit the study at any time without indicating any reasons [by closing the browser window], even before agreeing to this consent form. If I decide to quit the study before it is finished, I will still receive 50% of the monetary compensation. After completion of the study, I have the right to be informed about the background, aims and results of the study. I am aware that I can assert this right by asking for the relevant information. The corresponding contact address will be indicated at the end of the study. My anonymity will remain assured at all times. Data will be used for scientific purposes only and will be saved only for data analysis. Conclusions regarding individual participants are not possible. My anonymous data will be made available for secondary use by third parties in order to ensure transparency in science. The aim, purpose and extent of this secondary use are not yet foreseeable.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you have read and understood the above-mentioned points and consent to the terms of participation, please<br \/>\n&nbsp;<strong>type the word yes&nbsp;into the text box below<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>and click on &ldquo;Continue&rdquo;<\/strong>.<br \/>\nIf you do not agree, simply close this window.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/div>","QuestionType":"TE","SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"Selector":"SL","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CustomValidation","MinChars":"1","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID32\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Basic information on data protection Generally, we assess and process your data only after your c...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Text Response<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> yes <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID32\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID32","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID32","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"yes","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"IC failure","libraryID":"UR_56E3qwoIP9j8Xnn","messageID":"MS_erC4F2I5MLsS6do","subMessageID":"VE_CUSTOM_VALIDATION_0"}}}},"QuestionJS":false}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6liMpvgIS8eOlP8","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"Q